OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,FITV News Meridian's Andy Dickenson
OL,8,Freports on the workshop targeted and
OL,9,Fefforts to stop other traders falling
OL,10,Fvictim to tool theft
OL,12,FA cabinet maker from Sussex has spoken
OL,13,Fof his shock after thieves ransacked
OL,14,Fhis workshop.
OL,16,FThose responsible made off with tools
OL,17,Fworth tens of thousands of pounds
OL,18,Fbelonging to Steven Brand and his
OL,19,Fcolleagues.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,FSome of the equipment had been
OL,8,Fspecially made, unique for the self-
OL,9,Femployed company owners, with drawers
OL,10,Fripped out and locked boxes broken
OL,11,Finto last week.
OL,13,FSteven said some of his team have been
OL,14,Fleft with nothing, "I woke up in the
OL,15,Fmorning and saw that the WhatsApp
OL,16,Fgroup for work obviously had a
OL,17,Fsignificant amount of messages inside.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,F"It's hard, I'd say at least three or
OL,8,Ffour of the guys that work, have
OL,9,Fnothing left at all. Most of us have
OL,10,Fgot young children and it sucks."
OL,12,FTool theft continues to have a major
OL,13,Fimpact on tradespeople across the UK,
OL,14,Fwith tens of thousands of incidents
OL,15,Freported every year.
OL,17,FAccording to figures obtained by
OL,18,FDirect Line 26,724 tool thefts were
OL,19,Freported to police forces across the
OL,20,FUK in 2025, equivalent to a theft
OL,21,Fevery 20 minutes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,FIt's thought three quarters of
OL,8,Ftradespeople say they have been a
OL,9,Fvictim of tool theft and almost a
OL,10,Fthird have been victim to it more than
OL,11,Fonce.
OL,13,FSussex's Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,14,Fhas been working with builders firm
OL,15,FTravis Perkins to help tradespeople
OL,16,Fmark up to 50 tools for free, which
OL,17,Fcan act as a deterrent to thieves and
OL,18,Fmake them easier to track down if
OL,19,Fstolen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,FFollowing an event in Portslade on
OL,8,FTuesday, similar open days are taking
OL,9,Fplace in Horsham and Eastbourne as
OL,10,Fpart of the partnership.
OL,12,FPCC Katy Bourne said, "Co-funding
OL,13,F1,000 SelectaDNA tool marking kits in
OL,14,Fpartnership with Travis Perkins was an
OL,15,Feasy decision - time and again, I hear
OL,16,Fdevastating stories from tradespeople
OL,17,Fwhose livelihoods have been put at
OL,18,Frisk after having their tools stolen.
OL,26,@tD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,F"These kits will provide reassurance,
OL,8,Fpractical protection and a strong
OL,9,Fdeterrent to criminals, while also
OL,10,Fincreasing the chances that stolen
OL,11,Ftools can be reunited with their
OL,12,Frightful owners when recovered.
OL,14,F"I am delighted to be working
OL,15,Falongside Travis Perkins, building on
OL,16,Fmy longstanding efforts to support and
OL,17,Fprotect tradespeople across Sussex.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,F"I strongly encourage anyone working
OL,8,Fin a trade to attend one of our events
OL,9,Fto receive a free kit, capable of
OL,10,Fmarking up to 50 tools."
OL,12,FCarine Jessamine, Group Marketing and
OL,13,FDigital Director at Travis Perkins,
OL,14,Fsaid, "The risk of tool theft is
OL,15,Fconstantly in the minds of
OL,16,Ftradespeople across the country and we
OL,17,Fwant to do what we can to support
OL,18,Ftheir plight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,F"There are far too many tools stolen
OL,8,Fnationwide on a daily basis and it
OL,9,Fliterally stops tradespeople from
OL,10,Fbeing able to do their jobs in an
OL,11,Finstant.
OL,13,F"The impact of tool theft doesn't stop
OL,14,Fthere - it has all kinds of knock-on
OL,15,Feffects on the lives of those
OL,16,Faffected, whether that is their
OL,17,Ffinancial status or their mental
OL,18,Fwellbeing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,F"It is proven that tool marking acts
OL,8,Fas a deterrent to thieves so we are
OL,9,Fconfident this campaign will help to
OL,10,Fdecrease incidents of tool theft in
OL,11,Fthe area.
OL,13,FChief Inspector Oliver Fisher added,
OL,14,F"Our officers will continue to work
OL,15,Fclosely with local businesses, trade
OL,16,Fassociations and tradespeople to
OL,17,Frecover and return any reported stolen
OL,18,Fitems and to prevent these crimes
OL,19,Fbefore they happen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778609470
OL,3,CTradespeople left with nothing after
OL,4,C#60,000 of tools stolen in workshop
OL,5,Cransack
OL,7,F"We also know that stolen tools can be
OL,8,Fsold online and at boot fairs and we
OL,9,Fencourage the public not to buy
OL,10,Fvaluable tools if they have any
OL,11,Fconcerns about the provenance of the
OL,12,Ftool, or the person selling them.
OL,14,F"We encourage anyone who sees
OL,15,Fsuspicious activity to report it
OL,16,Fimmediately`this information could
OL,17,Fhelp us catch criminals in the act."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
